snippet.title: Yooka-Laylee E3 2016 Trailer!
snippet.description:
After months of toil and tease, we’re as chuffed as chips to finally release the Yooka-Laylee E3 2016 trailer into the wild!

Developed by Playtonic and published by Team17, Yooka-Laylee stars the charismatic new buddy duo Yooka and Laylee, who use an arsenal of special moves to explore – and expand – gorgeous 3D worlds filled with collectibles to discover, secrets to unlock and a cast of quirky characters to meet (or defeat). 

Yooka-Laylee has a firm release window of Q1 2017 on PC and consoles!

Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17Ltd
Follow Playtonic Games on Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlaytonicGames

Team17, founded in 1990, are a fully independent Video Game Developer and Games Label, responsible for the Worms™ series, Beyond Eyes, Sheltered and  many more. Ensure you never miss out on our latest videos by subscribing to us now: http://bit.ly/SubTeam17

Don't forget you can also Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/
